                    "paragraphTitle": "Saroo Brierley",
                    "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                    "paragraphContents": [
                        "Saroo Brierley was born in Ganesh Talai, a suburb in Khandwa, India. His family was poor and regularly had to beg for food and money."
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "paragraphOrdinal": 2,
                    "paragraphTitle": null,
                    "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                    "paragraphContents": [
                        "When he was five, Saroo took a train with his older brother, Ghuddu, from Khandwa to the city of Burhanpur, where Ghuddu had a job cleaning trains at night."
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "paragraphOrdinal": 3,
                    "paragraphTitle": null,
                    "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                    "paragraphContents": [
                        "By the time they arrived, Saroo was so tired he fell asleep on the platform. Ghuddu told him to wait there but when he didn't return, Saroo grew impatient and got on a train that was waiting at the platform. He fell asleep and when he woke up, he realized that he had traveled to Kolkata by mistake – 1,500 km away from home."
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "paragraphOrdinal": 4,
                    "paragraphTitle": null,
                    "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                    "paragraphContents": [
                        "After living on the streets for three weeks, he was placed in a local orphanage. An Australian family adopted him and he spent the next 25 years living in Australia. Saroo wanted to find his family. Using his memories and Google Earth, Saroo eventually found his hometown in India."
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "paragraphOrdinal": 5,
                    "paragraphTitle": null,
                    "paragraphSubtitles": null,
                    "paragraphContents": [
                        "Before his story was turned into an internationally successful book and movie, Saroo helped his dad run a business. Now he is working as a motivational speaker until he decides what to do next. Since living in Australia, Saroo has had a happy life and always feels lucky."
                    ]
                }
            ],
